title: Georgia, Sonja, Özgür and Loukas – Saca Chispas
_filename: Georgia, Sonja, Özgür and Loukas – Saca Chispas-TI_c9J0VCEU.mp4
description:
Georgia Priskou and Loukas Balokas, and Sonja Schüssler and Özgür Arin dance “Saca Chispas” by Julio De Caro, sung by Luis Díaz, at the 1st Sultans of Istanbul Tango Festival 2016 in Istanbul, Turkey.
